tachyon.client.block

Class BlockInStream

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.io.InputStream
      • tachyon.client.block.BlockInStream
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, AutoCloseable, BoundedStream, Seekable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BufferedBlockInStream, UnderStoreBlockInStream

    public abstract class BlockInStream
extends InputStream
implements BoundedStream, Seekable
    This class represents a stream to a block in the Tachyon system. The data source of the block could be a local Tachyon worker, a remote Tachyon worker, or the under storage system. All block streams provide data access to a sequential region of data of the block size of the block.
